In this project, we will implement a program that simulates Langton\rquote s Ant. For explanation please read it on Wikipedia:  {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Langton%27s_ant"}}{\fldrslt{\ul\cf1 https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Langton%27s_ant}}}\f0\fs22  (Links to an external site.). Note that the Langton\rquote s Ant simulation can be considered as a cellular automaton, a model that has simple rules governing its replication or destruction.\par
